{"tid":2342630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"崩潰！長髮女餐廳外排隊入席 「屎從天降」正中頭頂","createTime":"2020-12-27T09:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T10:10:18.000Z","uid":88743,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2c62dbdcaf199dd88d57b44d3d70049a23cd1c","tid":2342630,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3393673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3393673&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=a3e86cb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3393673&h=88b9f322\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3393673</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/12/27/phpsYuggj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2FphpsYuggj.jpg&h=8689c455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"blue\"><strong><ins>外國</ins></strong></span>1名長髮女子近日外出用餐，在室外排隊等候入席之際，突然「屎從天降」正中她的頭頂與身體其他部位，讓女子當場崩潰，事件曝光也讓網友們嘖嘖稱奇。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《新浪廣西》報導，<span class=\"blue\"><strong><ins>廣西壯族自治區南寧市</ins></strong></span>1名長髮女子，在當地1個社區的1間餐廳排隊等候用餐，突然1坨屎從空中墜下正中女子的頭髮與肩膀，她對此相當崩潰，當下也無法分辨究竟是人類還是動物的糞便，而餐廳業者則表示，「這已經不是第一次出現高空墜物了，之前墜落的東西也是五花八門。」<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，這起事件發生在本月24日，該處社區的服務中心指出，高空無法進行監控，因此要揪出丟屎的兇手相當不易，且安裝攔截網還需要獲得其他屋主同意，因此目前只能設置告示牌加以提醒民眾。<br />\n<br />\n許多中國網友知悉此事，都認為女子十分「好運」，紛紛留言指出「挨家挨戶做DNA比對」、「好沒有素質」、「有沒有公德心啊」、「我覺得就是他們可能吃飯太吵了，吵到了樓上，然後樓上就丟東西」、「家裡沒廁所嗎？這，過分了吧」、「把整個社區告上法院」、「這幫人都住在沒建廁所的房子裡嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7620df3db4848ac5430a265507d3435838cb69","tid":2342630,"uid":367959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:18:43.000Z","msg":"仲以為靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67b68a634431a526c84ae0d3fa0caf9e841e0f2","tid":2342630,"uid":67746,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"哪兒來的屎"},{"pid":"17437fca7180d247319722792701e77cd182eeef","tid":2342630,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"袓蝈回歸中世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e30178cd32aeca653274be4333bb88c474d99ac","tid":2342630,"uid":174445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"應該仲好痛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4f3aee3519ef6799eeb0b5a40af9969b975aaa","tid":2342630,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"一邊一國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b9a008737982ae3a25f5ce0da62f5e863fea9b","tid":2342630,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩 玩屎"},{"pid":"3f57b772e0e7329aea26080d1f931438879d0f5d","tid":2342630,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17437fca7180d247319722792701e77cd182eeef","tid":2342630,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"袓蝈回歸中世紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7b7d23e11ffaa764f246f6d5b0320b6c8aebd5","tid":2342630,"uid":98030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你個 surface area 咁大咩"},{"pid":"369597cac83a6c1a1efcad7f618f4198e7431a9e","tid":2342630,"uid":8636,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T10:06:47.000Z","msg"